HELP_MSG:
$help - to get help.

$quote - to get random quote.

$namo n - to get n random namo meme.(max=10)

$noods - to get random nood.

$menu - to get menu.

$say:[Text you wanna convter] - converts given text to speech.

$gif - to get quoted video as gif.

$sticker - to get quoted image as sticker.

$ping - pings time and info about chanka.

$memes n - to get n number of memes.(max=10,n default = 1)

$sr sunredditname n - to get n number of post from given subreddit.(max=10,n default = 1)
